title.rendered: Eldeco Centre Modern Office & Retail Hub | Saket

content.rendered:
Eldeco Centre Is A Buzzing Modern Office And Retail Hub

An Edifice That Makes An International Statement

• Ultra modern building with office and retail space on >3 acres plot from Delhi Metro Rail Corporation (DMRC)• Located in the heart of South Delhi, it is located at the junction of Saket and Malviya Nagar Metro Stations• Leasehold building with a single developer/operator• Only land parcel available in South Delhi for office development

An Address That Speaks For Itself

  • Located in the heart of South Delhi, next to Malviya Nagar Metro Station
  • Multiple hotels like Sheraton, Hilton, and Country Inn are located within a radius of 2 km
  • Green cover close to site is better than the city average with a Golf Course nearby
  • Prestigious Max Super Speciality Hospital
  • High-pedigree population catchment
  • High-end retail & office complexes near the vicinity like Select City Walk, DLF Place, South Court, Southern Park, Rectangle I, MGF Metropolitan Mall, Malviya Nagar, Geetanjali High Street, Anupam Shopping Complex, Saket

Well-appointed Office Spaces With a Retail Hub In Eldeco Centre

  • Class-A office space with luxury retail on the ground floor
  • Triple-layered window panes that maintain a constant temperature while allowing maximum natural light to filter in
  • Centre edifice to enjoy natural light and outside views
  • Automated parking management system. Basement and open parking with 1 car park per 500 Sq.ft of lease area
  • Centralized core with world-class 18 (approx.) meter atrium lobby
  • Efficient, column-free plates with a more usable area
  • IGBC-rated green building
  • Provision for additional fresh air in case any individual floor wants 100% fresh air

Management System At Eldeco Centre

• Central air handling on each floor• Retractable automated bollards with guardrooms• Full tracking mechanism for monitoring and local protection• CCTV camera surveillance• Security screening area in the building• Key electronic proximity card• Key access to tenant elevators at both lobby levels• Electric vehicle-friendly parking• Pre-fitted for wireless coverage

Designed For Safe Working Environment

  • The soaring atrium walls bestowing grandeur to the reception area add spaciousness and depth while open common areas will allow for better social distancing.
  • Separate air handling unit (AHU) on each floor so that the fresh air circulation does not get mixed between two offices.
  • 8 High capacity elevators instead of the mandatory requirement of 4 elevators to handle rush hour movement while maintaining required social distancing.
  • Designed for maximum natural light penetration with openable windows for ventilation.

Highlights of Eldeco Centre

  • Total Super area of Building – 2 Lac Sq.ft.
  • Area Available for Lease – 1.4 Lac sq. ft.
  • Rent for Office Space – 180 SQFT
  • Rent for Retail – 400 SQFT
  • CAM – 26 SQFT
  • 325 No. of car parking (surface & basements)
  • 2010 KVA Approx. (DG Capacity)

An Emphasis On Sustainability And Eco-friendliness

• Solar Glass Skylight• HVAC System – Chiller system delivering 6.2 co-efficient ofperformance (higher cooling per unit of energy)• Geothermal Cooling System• Heat recovery wheel allowing more fresh air• Lower operating cost of equipment• LEED Certified building

About The Promoters

Eldeco Infrastructure & Properties is a leading real estate developer in North India• Vast experience in real estate development with group housing, township development, shopping mall, office buildings, industrial parks, etc.• Multi-city presence (15 cities)

PROJECT HIGHLIGHTS OF ELDECO CENTRE

♕Ultra-Modern Building With Office & Retail Spaces

♕Custom Spaces Available For Retail & Office Space

♕2Lakh+ sqft Gross Leasable Area

♕325 No. Of Car Parking Spaces

♕Lift – 8 Nos. (HIGH SPEED & DESTINATION CONTROL SYSTEM)

♕Automated parking management system.

♕Basement and open car parking space

♕Centralized core with world-class 18 (approx.) meter atrium lobby

♕IGBC-rated green building

♕Full tracking mechanism for monitoring and local protection

♕CCTV camera surveillance

♕Security screening area in the building

♕Key electronic proximity card

♕Key access to tenant elevators at both lobby levels

♕Electric vehicle-friendly parking

Don’t miss the opportunity to get your #commercial space at the only land parcel available in South Delhi for office development.

Lalit Kaushik
